<A>__{the chapel is deserted inside. in the dim light we can see a form stretched out on the floor. it is ben. he begins to stir a little as if just beginning to come to after being knocked unconscious.}
<L>__{exterior ambrose chapel (day) med. close shot}
<A>__{the policemen are grouped around the patrol car, as patterson, the sergeant, talks over a radio telephone.}
